# test2000.cns — synthetic test scene, ~2000 nodes with edges
# Five major groups, up to 4 levels deep. Same arrangements as test1000
# at roughly double the size. Edge thicknesses are auto-clamped to
# at most half the diameter of the smaller endpoint node.

